Package ar.edu.utn.frc.tup.lc.iv.services

Interface IAuthRangeService

All Known Implementing Classes:
AuthRangeService
public interface IAuthRangeService
Service interface for managing authorized ranges. This interface defines the methods for handling operations related to authorized ranges, including creating, updating, retrieving, and deleting authorized ranges.
